text: Utah State Route 13 may refer to: * Utah State Route 13, a state highway in Box Elder County in northern Utah, United States * Utah State Route 13 (1962-1977), the former state designation for a section of U.S. Route 89 in Cache and Rich counties in northern Utah, United States * Utah State Route 13 (1912-1962), a former state highway in Millard and Sevier counties in central Utah, United States, most of which is also known as Clear Creek Canyon Road ==See also== * List of state highways in Utah * List of highways numbered 13
title: Utah State Route 13 (disambiguation)
